name: fd
review: it's very oily. it doesn't stay even for one minute

name: B
review: This is easy to use & lasts all day

name: Bee bop
review: One swipe was all it took

name: judykoby
review: I decided to go back to blonde eyebrows because I thought that the brown was too dark for my complexion.  This is not the correct color for me.  The pencil seems to work fine and it stays on all day without fading.  I have had to doctor it up some because the color needed to be darker.  So don't take this as the pencil is bad...just the blonde color on me.  I took back one blonde after buying two and traded it in for the brown which was not in stock when I went in to buy it.  This is the closest to the Ulta brow "chubby" that I used to use which they have now discontinued.  Once I have used the brown I will make another statement about the pencil.

name: My Mom
review: It looks like a thin fake layer of color on my face.

name: Brown Eyes
review: It goes on light which is a good thing.

name: Sue
review: Returning for a refund. I would give this zero stars if allowed.

name: Denise
review: Unfortunately, this color didn't' work with my eyebrow color.  I'm a redhead and this was too light.  I had to return this eyebrow pencil.

name: Morgan
review: I have very thick eyebrows. I just have to fill them in because they can be scarce. This product was so greasy. It made my eyebrows wet. I chose it originally because I liked that it was a thicker stick and not a tiny skinny one. But it was not good for my brows!

name: Tam
review: Not what I expected, I have to add brow powder to get desired color.

name: heather
review: I decided to try this after years of using the Revlon brow product with pencil on one side and wand/gel on the other side (I get tired of the mess of sharpening the pencil and the pencil would run out before the gel). I like this product, it does a good job filling in my thin brows. I will probably be buying a small brow comb because I miss not being able to smooth and shape my brows after applying color.

name: kady
review: For folks with wide brows only
